Flow.description: When a Test Run is created in the Integration Test Utility App, this flow will check to see if the Email for the User that created the Test Run matches a SOT User record. If so, the flow will complete the User lookup field on the SOT User record and then update the Progress Note Signing details on the Assigned Site record for that SOT User.
